{"title":"「一本通 3.1 练习 2」构造完全图","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["最小生成树"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/10067#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=10067","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/10067/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/10067/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/10067"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于完全图 $G$，若有且仅有一棵最小生成树为 $T$，则称完全图 $G$ 是树 $T$ 扩展出的。\r\n\r\n给你一棵树 $T$，找出 $T$ 能扩展出的边权和最小的完全图 $G$。\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行 $N$ 表示树 $T$ 的点数；\r\n\r\n接下来 $N-1$ 行三个整数 $S_i, T_i, D_i$；描述一条边 $(S_i, T_i)$ 权值为 $D_i$；\r\n\r\n保证输入数据构成一棵树。\r\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出仅一个数，表示最小的完全图 $G$ 的边权和。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n4  \r\n1 2 1  \r\n1 3 1  \r\n1 4 2  \r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n12\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例说明\r\n添加 $D(2, 3)=2, D(3, 4)=3, D(2, 4)=3$ 即可。"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $20\\%$ 的数据，$N\\le 10$；  \r\n对于 $50\\%$ 的数据，$N\\le 1000$；  \r\n对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，$N\\le 10^5, 1\\le D_i\\le 10^5$。\r\n"}]}